And IRT guild officers not answering questions from guildmates. As an officer I always take the time to address any issue by a guildie, even if I think it's a waste of time. It's called being a good leader and showing your guildies you care. I don't know Torm from Adam but if an officer treated me the way it has been reported here I would have /guildremove in a second.<br>
